trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection"></xref> class represents any partial results returned from a not-yet-completed asynchronous operation.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection.Contains(System.Object)"></xref> method determines whether this <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection"></xref> object contains a specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> for which to search.
`true` if the specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref> is part of the collection or `false` if it is not.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection.CopyTo(System.Object[],System.Int32)"></xref> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
A one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection"></xref> object.
The zero-based index of values where copying begins.
values is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
index is less than zero.
values is multidimensional
-or-
The number of elements in the source is greater than the available space from index to the end of the destination values.
The type of the source cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination values.

The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection.IndexOf(System.Object)"></xref> method returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence of the specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref> in the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> for which the index is returned.
The index value of the specified <xref href="System.Object"></xref>, if found, or -1 if the specified object is not found.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.PartialResultsCollection.Item(System.Int32)"></xref> property contains the <xref href="System.Object"></xref> at the specified index.
The index value of the <xref href="System.Object"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> at the specified index.
index is less than zero or index is equal to or greater than the number of items in the collection.
